flowchart TD
    Start([User Initiates Creation]) --> InitScript{Run init_plugin.py}
    
    InitScript -->|Input: Name & Path| CreateDir[Create Plugin Directory]
    CreateDir --> CheckExists{Exists?}
    
    CheckExists -->|Yes| Error[Error: Directory Exists]
    CheckExists -->|No| Struct[Generate Structure]
    
    Struct --> Manifest[Create .claude-plugin/plugin.json]
    Struct --> SkillsDir[Create skills/ Directory]
    
    SkillsDir --> SampleSkill[Create Sample Skill]
    SampleSkill --> SkillMD[Generate SKILL.md Template]
    
    Manifest --> Done([Creation Complete])
    SkillMD --> Done
    
    Done --> NextSteps[Next Steps]
    NextSteps --> EditManifest[1. Edit Manifest]
    NextSteps --> EditSkill[2. Edit SKILL.md]
    NextSteps --> AddResources[3. Add Resources]
    
